Our Company


            American Railcar Industries, Inc. is a prominent North American manufacturer of railcars with an emerging global presence. ARI is proud to be one of the largest producers of quality railcars built in the United States. We are an ambitious, purpose driven organization with dynamic growth objectives. Our expanding railcar product line is complimented by an extensive railcar repair network and engineering consulting services. ARI manufactures a comprehensive range of parts and products for rail and industrial applications.
        

            We structure our organization to support a team of innovative people who strive daily to make a positive impact by providing solutions for our customers and success for our stakeholders.  We value integrity, quality, commitment, innovation and team work, and conduct our business within the highest ethical standards.
        



Our Culture


            We structure our organization to support a team of innovative people who strive daily to make a positive impact by providing solutions for our customers and success for our stakeholders.
            Our high expectations are clearly communicated and we encourage healthy debate to address the challenges and opportunities of our business.
        

            We value integrity, quality, commitment, innovation and team work, and conduct our business within the highest ethical standards.
            We believe that with great achievement comes great responsibility.
        

            ARI operates under the principles of LEAN Manufacturing. The LEAN Initiative is based on three simple objectives; Create Value, Eliminate Waste and Continuous Improvement. LEAN is a process and a commitment that is on-going.
            The LEAN Initiative helps ensure that our manufacturing facilities provide a superior work environment with an outstanding safety record.
        

            ARI requires a diverse workforce with employees trained in a broad spectrum of disciplines.
        



Our Benefits


            American Railcar Industries offers competitive benefits and programs to help employees and their families meet their healthcare and retirement planning needs.
            The various benefits offered to employees based on eligibility may include:
        

            Medical 
            Dental 
            Vision 
            Employee Assistance Program (EAP) 
            Paid time off (vacation) 
            Paid Holidays 
            Life Insurance 
            Long Term Disability 
            Voluntary Accidental Death and Dismemberment (AD & D) Insurance 
            Travel Accident Insurance 
            401(k) Plan with company match
            Education assistance
        


American Railcar Industries, Inc. is an equal opportunity employer. New hires for United States base positions must furnish proof of their right to work.







