Tank Cars

    ARI has flexible and vertically integrated manufacturing facilities that can produce multiple railcar types.
    ARI's railcar design and manufacturing capabilities extend beyond our list of standard products. 







                        American Railcar Industries, Inc. builds the full spectrum of DOT class tank cars for the transportation of liquid products.
                        Tank cars are the most diverse of all freight car designs and the most challenging to design and build.
                        ARI is proud to boast of our history. We are the oldest manufacturer with over 150 years of tank car design and manufacturing experience and the only builder
                        that still manufactures our product in the United States. Whether you are shipping vegetable oil, fuel oil, or specialty chemicals, ARI can design and build a railcar with exceptional quality & reliability.
                    






